nacle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shilton_and_Barnacle\"}, {\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.181551174772619e-23, \"text\": \"Ronald Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ron_Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6534705937381894, \"rank\": 0.5290477601691277, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1173, \"end\": 1186, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Philip Snyman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13415036\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philip_Snyman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are ready,\\\" said Snyman.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1351, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had a good week of preparation since we arrived here, which included a good training session against Uruguay two days ago.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1478, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1457, \"end\": 1464, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uruguay_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.999997839753692, \"rank\": 1.8191466129204345e-06, \"text\": \"Uruguay\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uruguay_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uruguay_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That helped us a lot, as a match is always better than just training as a squad.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We saw different pictures on attack and defence and had to adapt accordingly.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a well worth exercise and sharpened us up nicely for the matches against Ireland and New Zealand.\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1744, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1720, \"end\": 1727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996912265, \"rank\": 1.6655282771526255e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1732, \"end\": 1743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.99999999965803, \"rank\": 3.368591232985352e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For us, it will just be another opportunity to represent our country and to deliver our best effort for the jersey,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yes, the reward might be different, but the game remains the same and that is where our focus will be tomorrow.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Both Ireland and New Zealand are the same in style and approach.\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2053, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1994, \"end\": 2001, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996912265, \"rank\": 1.6655282771526255e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2006, \"end\": 2017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.99999999965803, \"rank\": 3.368591232985352e-10, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are bigger than us and more physical and will attack our breakdown in order to slow us down.\", \"from\": 2054, \"to\": 2151, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have real magic and speed on the outside and teams will try and prevent us to use that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2243, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snyman said their defensive effort will be crucial if they want to start on a positive note.\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ireland is our main focus for now, we want to start well and lay a foundation for the rest of the tournament,\\\" said Snyman.\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2340, \"end\": 2347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996912265, \"rank\": 1.6655282771526255e-10, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ireland_national_rugby_union_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need to make our tackles and put pressure on their attackers.\", \"from\": 2465, \"to\": 2530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are a dangerous side when they have momentum, so we need to stop them for getting going.\\\"\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2625, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2706, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2627, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WIN_Television\", \"score\": 0.9999987866725035, \